        "text": "三农业区位分析",
        "bbox": [
          0.10692701069270107,
          0.38735177865612647,
          0.2807996280799628,
          0.4077733860342556
        ],
        "order": 5
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103_5",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "1.灌溉农业区位分析",
        "bbox": [
          0.12273361227336123,
          0.41699604743083,
          0.34774523477452346,
          0.43873517786561267
        ],
        "order": 6
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103_6",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "典型地区：宁夏平原.河套平原.河西走廊、南疆等",
        "bbox": [
          0.1413296141329614,
          0.4479578392621871,
          0.6276150627615062,
          0.47101449275362317
        ],
        "order": 7
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103_7",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "分析自然区位因素：热量充足，温差大：地形平坦：土壤肥沃：灌溉水源充足 不足：水资源短缺：冬季受寒潮和暴风雪影响；土壤的盐碱化等",
        "bbox": [
          0.1413296141329614,
          0.47891963109354413,
          0.8637842863784286,
          0.5322793148880105
        ],
        "order": 8
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103_8",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "2.商品谷物农业 典型地区：东北地区 分析区位因素",
        "bbox": [
          0.11715481171548117,
          0.5731225296442688,
          0.3412366341236634,
          0.6574440052700923
        ],
        "order": 9
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103_9",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "(1)自然因素：温带季风气候，夏季高温多雨，雨热同期：地形平坦开阁：耕地面积 广大：土壤肥沃：水源充足。",
        "bbox": [
          0.09576940957694095,
          0.6666666666666666,
          0.9186424918642492,
          0.7206851119894598
        ],
        "order": 10
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103_10",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "(2)社会经济因素：地广人稀，农产品商品率高；生产规模大.机械化水平高：交通 便利：市场广阔：工业比较发达：国家政策支持。",
        "bbox": [
          0.09576940957694095,
          0.7285902503293807,
          0.9139934913993492,
          0.7839262187088274
        ],
        "order": 11
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103_11",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "不足：热量不足：土地沙化、水工流失加剧：土壤肥力下降：冬季受寒潮和冻害的 影响等。",
        "bbox": [
          0.09483960948396095,
          0.7905138339920948,
          0.9121338912133892,
          0.8438735177865613
        ],
        "order": 12
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103_12",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "与美国商品谷物农业比较：",
        "bbox": [
          0.1506276150627615,
          0.8544137022397892,
          0.41562064156206413,
          0.8761528326745718
        ],
        "order": 13
      }
    ]
